            <title>[LUCENE-3879] fix more position corrumptions in 4.0 codecs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3879</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Spinoff of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3876&quot; title=&quot;TestIndexWriterExceptions fails (reproducible)&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUCENE-3876&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Some codecs have invalid asserts, wrong shift operators etc.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If a position exceeds Integer.MAX_VALUE/2 and then also has a payload,&lt;br/&gt;
it will produce corrumpt indexes or other strange errors.&lt;/p&gt;

